    <mxCell id="df2" value="Q2: What is the conflict resolution strategy?&#xa;&#xa;No strategy defined → Do not use shared state&#xa;Last write wins → Document it explicitly&#xa;Field-level authority → Define per field, per agent" style="rounded=1;arcSize=3;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#E8F5E9;strokeColor=#81C784;strokeWidth=1;fontSize=11;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontColor=#1B5E20;" vertex="1" parent="1">
