    <mxCell id="df3" value="Q3: What happens if an agent fails mid-write?&#xa;&#xa;No answer → Do not use shared state without a transaction model&#xa;Idempotent writes possible → Document retry strategy&#xa;Non-idempotent → Require lock/commit/rollback semantics" style="rounded=1;arcSize=3;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#E8F5E9;strokeColor=#81C784;strokeWidth=1;fontSize=11;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontColor=#1B5E20;" vertex="1" parent="1">
